title: NFS Most Wanted 2005 [v1.3 TOOLS]
description:
Tools for Need For Speed: Most Wanted 2005




Instructions:

1. Install game using working key and you have also FFF214 keygen.
2. Copy "Patch.v1.3" into game base directory and RUN IT, default:

on x64 Windows (C:Program Files (x86)EA GAMESNeed for Speed Most Wanted)
on x86 Windows (C:Program FilesEA GAMESNeed for Speed Most Wanted)

3. Copy "INGAMEC.BUN" into "GLOBAL" folder (unlocks Black Edition content).
4. Copy crack into game installation folder.
5. Copy "NFSMW_Custom_Res_Changer" folder content into game installation folder.

6. Have fun and seed! ;)
